values:
friend ko si aehr pero naiirita ako sa kanila. well last sunday, i was miserable. pati nung monday and tuesday... i can't stop crying. natutulala ako... now, i guess i'm better. medyo napapaisip and medyo bitter. pero in fairness, mabilis ako makarecover. apir to myself! congrats! 

come to think of it, ang dami na palang signs... ung book ni catwoman sa national nung tuesday, finals week...dec 14. tapos pti nung wed... tapos nawala na lang 1 day... tapos ung my sassy girl nung dec 15 na from lemon. tapos ung mga kanta around me... ung kay kitchie na "wag na wag mong sasabihin" ung sa session road na "suntok sa buwan" ung super lss ko lately na "i'll be over you" from toto... tapos ung bihirang pagtext at pagcall at pagkikita... lahat un... too late na nung ma-realize ko. kaya pala hindi na nya masyado ipinilit ung panaginip ko nung dec 11. ang lungkot lungkot ko before kse namimiss ko na sya. we were a millimeter close to us being "us" kaso un nga nagfly un... pti si alexander the great...

wala na ung "rain" ko. ung "pillow" ko. ung kanta kong "panaginip." pero kanta ko pa din un! ung # fan ko sa "prettykat" wala na lahat un... wala na ung "phonepal" ko. ung "textmate" ko. hayyy... ang sad... pero it's all true...

sana lang hindi nagkamali si sid sa naging desisyon niya. as for now, f. o. muna kme ni aehr. o well... di ko sya ma-take! naiimbyerna ako! as for sid, i'm still praying na sana bumalik sya sakin. i'd still say YES. kung sakaling mawala ung luv ko sa kanya at marealize nya na ako pala dapat, sori na lang. sid, i don't know if i want you to be happy or not. as for now, i wish that u are mine. i want u to be mine but i want u to be happy. i don't know... i'm confused. and i also want you to realize na ikaw ang nawalan at hindi ako.

i hope my fairytale will end happy with the guy who deserves my tears, my love, my friends, and the whole of me. because i know that i deserve that guy as well. a guy worth loving, worth fighting, and worth crying but would never make me cry. a guy worth waiting for.

wala lang. malungkot lang ako. sinaktan ako ni sid ng di nya alam. nandito ako sa netopia at gusto kong umiyak. mamaya na lang siguro sa bahay.

sa totoo lang... ang hirap ng confused. i really hate this feeling. hindi ako makapag-isip ng tama. ang pinakatherapy ko ay magnet at magjournal. kahit na kanino ko sabihin walang magiging solution. sana pwede ko na lang sabihin sa mukha ng ibang tao jan ung gusto kong mangyari at sana gusto rin nya un pero syempre hindi ko kaya. if someone would ask me what he/she should do, my advice to that person is to go for what he/she desires. pero it is not applicable to me. never.

oo i admit, i like the guy. love? i'm not sure...but i'm getting there... definitely! awww... yeah i know! how stupid am i to fall for a guy who doesn't want to commit to anyone right now! and how stupid could i get to feel awkward around him! damn! i hate him... arrrrgggghhhhhhhhhh!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! o well... life is a BIATCH!

frankly, the whole day i've been praying to see him and have a chat with him, bond with him, and just be me. akala ko hindi ko sya makikita kse parang kahit anung pilit ko na puntahan sya sa mga possible places na andun sya... it seemed like he is nowhere to be found! pero syempre, expect the unexpected. on our way out of mapua, i ran into dell who was on her way to pavi. tapos aun e d sama din ako sa pavi. e medyo blurred ang vision ko...i wasn't able to see them. mga tao. andun pla si ano! ayyyy!!!!!!!!!!!!! hindi ko lam kung anu gagawin ko. nahihiya talaga ako. i was calm but a little silent. o life!!!!!!! shit! pag gusto mo un ang nafefeel diba? pag mahal mo u can be yourself... i was myself(partly) kasi may silent moments talaga ako. and i wasn't kse may gusto nga ako. i really feel sad right now... pwede umiyak?

iiiyak ko na lang siguro ito. you know why my font is blue?it's because that is what i feel right now. gusto ko magfocus sa positive outlook ko pero parati ko naiisip itong sitwasyon ko. it is really hard for me kse hindi ko na alam ang ganitong feeling. parang napaka-naive ko kung tutuusin... pero sino nga ba ang hindi nagiging tanga pagdating sa mga ganitong bagay, aber?

mahirap na masarap pero masakit ang magkagusto... at malala, magmahal. we all say that life is what you make it. you are in control of your own life. and love... is destined to happen. love is fate. love is uncontrollable because it happens for a lot of reason and after the battle, we would find ourselves tired but relieved, emotionally frustrated but at the end, happy. love is unpredictable and you can't do anything about it because you are not in control whether you like it or not. pero diba love is life and life is love? i guess, we live life by taking a part of it and some just letting it be. o what the heck! i'm confused!

malamang umaasa lang ako sa wala. hindi pala malamang... talagang wala!

ako'y malungkot nanaman. hayyy bat ba ganito? un know what??? i hate you! arrrggggggggghhhhhhhhhh!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! i found this amazing guy sa ym tapos parang naddivert na ung attention ko sa kanya and i've recently concluded na we(ikaw+ako hindi ako+sya) are better off as friends. yup just friends. kse though i'm not in love with you and though i might be falling, i felt na hindi mo ko mamahalin tulad ng pagmamahal na maaari kong ibigay sayo. and last monday, i felt so happy. everything seemed so well. tapos parang okay na sakin ung situation na we're just friends. that thing sa pavi, nung nagtext ka pa sakin, i thought na it's so nice of you. pati kahapon(gabi) at kanina. so sweet of you to remember. tapos we saw each other kanina and i really looked forward to that event na though unexpected, it felt good kasi i saw you and i know na kahit ang pwede ko lang i-expect sayo ay friendship, deep down i'm still hoping na hindi. i'm really confused right now. i've adapted and moved on... i came to my senses na and finally realized na hanggang dun na lang and okay na sakin because of this guy. pero right now i feel so sad... it's like i'm holding back to something, or should i say someone that i never had... hayyy... you're making me so confused and right now i want to cry. cry hard... dapat talaga i texted you na kanina e... the reason why i didn't kasi nga i thought i wouldn't regret. i thought that i'm over you. i thought na i fully reconciled with the "just friends" idea. pero un nga... hindi pa. omg! i miss you so much!!! sana tawagan mo naman ako. lam mo ba, sayo lang ako willing magpuyat till the time comes na we have to go to school na. i hate you so much i wanna kill you! naisip ko kse if we have "something" malamang nagseselos ka na sa new guy(na kung sa bagay, hindi ko rin naman masyado namemention). pero siguro ako lang nakakadama nun. sana bumalik na ko sa senses ko. hindi ko inaakalang maguupdate uli ako ng journal sa ganitong matters... i miss you and i'm really sad right now. i don't know. i get nervous around you. what could it be? hindi dapat ako nagkakaganito kasi ewan ko. i wana try pero i don't wana lose you. FYI, eto po sya. Goodluck!

kasalukuyan kong kausap si sid sa text. wala lang. tapos na kahapon ang kasal ng sister niya. badtrip talaga tong term na to! lahat na lang kapalpakan. kala ko dati tapos na ung mga badtrip days ko dahil sa subjects sa mapua. un pala until now meron pa din! syet! ay onga pala may nakiya ako nakadreads na nakared. ang cute niya grabe! hahaha! asus! tapos un nga... dumating ako ng school saktong 11. plan ko pa sana magremovals sa enercon around 11:15 kasi sayang ung opportunity. e itong si sir teresa ang tagal dumating! kaya un... in short di na ko nakahabol. chaka di rin kse ko nakapagreview so at first mejo okei lang. tapos pagdating ko dun sa room disaster kasi ang daming tao. syet! putangina talaga! sana nagmake-up na lang ako! i mean removal!!!!!!!!!!!!1 nakakafrustrate talaga! hayyy... hmpf!! super inisip ko talaga un nafrustrate talaga ako hanggang kanina. buti nga ngayon mejo nakarecover na ko. tapos onga pala ang tagal ng mga kagroup ko sa enercon! ako lang ata ang nandoon e. wala palang ata. ako nga lang sa group. pahamak talaga sila! syet! tapos un nakita ko na nga pala grade ko sa exam sa comlab. hayyy... sana lang talaga hindi ako bumagsak.

fast forward... pinagalitan ako ng dad ko dahil late ako umuwi dahil nagdinner kme ni tin. treat ko. ung dad ko super badtrip to the point na sabihan akong wag na daw ako mag-aral. E GAGO pala sya e!1 problema na nya un. hindi naman ako masyado affected kasi mas madami ako iniisip regarding school ngayon. madami akong mga dasal. sana hindi mabreak ung record ko. sana maipasa ko pa ung micro. chaka onga pla, the reason why tin and i took a lot of time eating at tokyo tokyo is  that we were talking about boys mainly sid, rj, and afos. hehehe

aun... kahapon(tuesday) nakaimbento kmeng bagong magkakapatid ng bagong kapatiran... ang villapera(which means na we are vere^infinity rich and also, it is common to us nga pala) obvious naman daw akording to jepo. dapat conio ka at madaming pera. original members are :moi,jepoy,migs,francis,chad, and mark. next time na kwento... break muna

it just came into a realization that my prospect, TRISTAN JOSEPH MAGPANTAY is already taken(i think). kasi, kanina tin and i went to the mall to eat new favorite food(chaofan--3rd time this week since monday). tapos i told her that in his profile nakalagay sa status is married. actually, i had doubts na before. it is not yet confirmed pero i have this gut feeling na. then kanina i asked my gud 'ol bud adrian(from circuits before) for his #. then i texted him by asking 4 jen's #. di sya nagreply!!!!!!!!!!!!! PUTANGINA!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

TAE SYA!!!!!!!!!!!! SYET!!!!!!!!!!!!! NAIINIS AKO SA KANYA!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

GOD please help me... finally, a man of my dreams, my hopes and my imagination(i think). Or maybe... a man who can fit my needs. honest to goodness, we're so similar. attitude wise, education wise, opinion wise, future wise.... yup we're compatible. Pero why does it have to be this way? GOD i'm confused. I really need your help. ewan ko ba kung bakit ang mga tulad ko madaling malaglag. tapos minsan pag lumalapit na ang gusto, bigla naman akong lalayo. tapos minsan pag alam mong gusto mo talaga, hindi naman pwede.

 

CONCLUSION : Sadyang mapaglaro ang tadhana.

ayun, ako ay batang sipunin. yup, i've got colds. o well... late ako nagising and i didn't study comm kse i watched so close last nyt. it was nice and i don't regret not being able to study... anyway, late akong nagising. i was a little disappointed but it's okei. i ate and run and rode an fx. i studied and before ako bumama, i the realized na di pa pala ako bayad. funny kse nagpapara na ako. pati driver natawa. HAHAHAHA!!!

ayun nagexam na and it payed off....... kaso kulang kse may mali pa din ako. syet! yup, may katangahan akong ginawa! may exam din ako sa consti kaya nag-aral ako during lunch. di na ko naglunch total d naman ako super gutom. nung nalaman kong may appli, nagpunta ako agad sa mms from apo at nanghassle kina debbie,monica,irra, and ainah! wahehehehe!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! senxa na sila kse natripan ko sila! ayun, c monic at debbie lang napirmahan ko. maarte ako e.

ayuz!

nagservice kme kanina. nothing astonishing. successful naman. di nadisperse lahat. ayun...umuulan pa at late halos lahat ng senior na brods... ayun... kasal din ni ramil ngaun... yun.... pagdating ko umalis pla silang lahat. sunod-sunod. ako na lang ang naiwan... un lang, mega surf na rin ako. friendster, email, at livejournal. di na nga ako nakanood ng luv2luv e. ayun. ayus!

 

mission: accomplished!

testimony: tapos!

ayun... i really didn't know what to do and it seemed like nobody was there for me... my friends, family, brothers and sisters, my batchmate, my ate ianne... lahat. i prayed na lang. i texted kati pero kala ko di sya magrereply... eventually, okei na kme. thank GOD talaga... when it seems like nobody's there, just pray. GOD will never leave your side. he is always there. thanks talaga... sya ang sandalan ko sa oras ng pangangailangan. okei na kme.

so far the ee-ece-coe outing was good. kinda dull pero we survived. un nga sa start pa lang pasaway na kme. sabi ni manong bawal daw stop overs... yet we stopped along magallanes because of 1 of our passengers. tapos a few hours later, while every1 was asleep, biglang nagstop si manong! pasaway talaga! shocked kme! hahaha... may gumaya pa ngang bus. ung sa micro. tapos nainis pa ung si BADET na taga sc... eventually umalis din sila. wala pa rin si manong. we were in panic already whe he showed up. tangna! jumebs pala! wahahaha... syet natahimik kmeng lahat. ayunnn....

 

hanggang sa gumating na kme sa resort. ang labo! ang gulo-gulo! nakapasok pa nga ako na hindi pinupunit ung ticket ko e... hahaha!!! pero bad3p un! kung alam ko lang! sayang ung 450... anyweiz, ayun... may nagnakaw ng cottage namin so we wer kinda stuck in a small umbrella(pero that's not what you call it... i forot na e). we were there at around 10:30 pero we settled at around 11. we ate sarahdel's spagetti first... yumyum! thanks dell! hahaha

 

then we got bored... e i was too lazy to change to swim pero michael is insisting me to change na... da heck! i'l change if i want to noh! get a life, please(joke. hehehe)... yun nga we got bored so we decided to start drinking na... emperador brandy courtesy of moi! ang kulit pa nga namin kasi bawat person na dumaan na kilala namin pinapatagay din namin. ayus! da best talaga ang mms kahit 2 lang kmeng representative ni dell, isang paulit-ulit na appli(michael), at isang adopted(rayner)

 

okei plang kasama sina anton. cool din. hahaha... a little later may nareceive akong text from sc... free food daw! e ang kapal ko... so punta naman ako at kain. syet! ang kapal ko talaga! e sayang e! besides, di naman libre ang ticket ko noh! tapos nun balik na kme sa so-called "cottage" namin. pag dating dun, lahat kme masakit ang ulo. nagdecide kme ni del na pumunta muna sa bus. pumayag naman si manong at natulog muna kmeng 3 dun nila rayner.

 

at around 3:30(startalk) nagising na kme. kain muna uli. tapos nood ng aladin. crush ko ung disney animation na un. after nun nagkaron ng typicaldrama ang cool couple na si sarahdel and rayner. ayun... humantong sa ako'y bumalik na sa resort at nagbihis at naghintay ng taong dadating kasi excited na ko lumangoy. ano ba un! malapit na mag-pack-up tapos di man lang ako makaka-swin? da hell!!!!!!!

 

mejo nawalan nga ako ng pakialam sa ibang tao. i was sitting still nung makita ko ang karamihan sa myembro ng organisasyong ASSets(cute ba? sexy yan... ass e hehehe).... salamat at nakita ko si tin... sumama muna ako sa kanilang "tour" at hinila ko na si tin sa pathetic na slides... pathetic talaga! anyway, nakapagslide kme 3 times. twice sa walang salbabida at once dun sa meron. nakakatawa kasi d first time around ayaw pang umusad pababa... na-stuck kme. dapat pla nakahiga para mabilis at malakas ang impact!

 

ayun... nung tapos na pila na sa shower room. ang haba at ang tagal! ung una ko pa plang napilahan e walang tubig sa shower room!! hahaha... e di pila ako uli... tapos un! ang tagal! nakalimutan ko pa kay del sa bus ung mga toiletries ko na binili ko sa 7-11. kung alam ko lang na manghihingi rin lang pala ako e di sana di nalang ako bumili! sayang lang ang 30 pesos ko dun! anyway, thanks to lirio at may nagamit ako.

 

after long waiting hours it's my turn na rin! after long bathing hours, it's their turn na rin! and guess what, ang onti na lang nila. halos last batch na rin pala kme kasi ung iba sa sink n lang nagshampoo and stuff. when i checked my stuff, i saw a few missed calls... tumatawag pla sina rayner at dell kasi kala nila i was missing. hahaha! they didn't know na i was just absent minded kasi ang tagal nga ng pila! sabi pa ni del e naiwan ko daw ung soap and shampoo ko sa bus. i told her na i asked for some from a friend and i'm finished already. i told her my location and when i opened the door, i looked at the left side. wala sila! pag-lingon ko sa right, may 2 guys na dumaan in front of me. 1 drunk and 1 na nagaalalay sa drunk. ung drunk na cute stopped over and we shook(or hold) hands(right). and guess what i said? i told him: You're drunk!

 

goodness! what a pathetic thing i said! ayun... after a few seconds ayan na sila dell... they handed me my stuff and told me to follow them sa bus na lang. gosh! buti na lang pretty ako nung mga panahong un! pretty in pink. on the way to the bus nasalubong ko pa sina eman. ayun same-old-same-old. nung nasa bus na ko magro-rol-call pa dapat kme pero when i asked them kung kumpleto na ba ang mga kasama nila and when they said yes, nagulat ako ng biglang umalis na kme. excited na si manong umalis! ayaw na ata niya ng attendance! hahaha...(baka nac-cr uli!)

 

matiwasay naman magpatakbo si manong. umalis kme around 6 at dumating aroung 8:30. di na nga pinasok sa loob ng intramuros ung bus. kakatawa. sa "shoulder" kse dinaan at super mag-over-take

 

>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>fast forward<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<

supposedly, hintay ko pa si tin. kala ko nakadating na sila pero mejo doubtful ako so wait ako(chaka ala kse kong kasabay). nang dumating na ang bus nila dennis, sumabay na ko kina dennis pauwi. around 9:30 ata un. chika-chika. i then found out na we had d best bus. yes! APIR! AYUZ! diretcho ako hospital. nagbantay at dun na natulog. ayun... de rest is history!
